leadership.name: Peter Pan
leadership.description: Our CEO, Peter, credits his hardworking East Asian immigrant parents who undertook the arduous journey to the shores of America with the intention of giving their children the best future. His mother"s wizardy in the fashion world by designing clothes with whatever is available inexpensively at the local stores, was his first inspiration to create the fusion clothes for which Beauty style became well known.

leadership.name: Dhanasekaran Witherspoon
leadership.description: Our CFO, Danny, as he is affectionately referred to by his colleagues, comes from a long established family tradition in farming and produce. His experiences growing up on a farm in the Australian outback gave him great appreciation for varieties of warm clothes. As he puts it in his own words, Everything that runs, wins, and everything that stays, pays!

leadership.name: Agumbe Tang
leadership.description: Blessed with the most discerning fashion sense, Agumbe, our CFO, personally ensures that every clothe that we sell meets his exacting desires. Our sellers ensures if our clothes does not meet his exacting standards. He lives by his motto, You click only if you survive my choices.

leadership.name: Jhon Munoz
leadership.description: Award winning three-star Michelin Seller with wide International experience having worked closely with whos-who in the fashion world, he specializes in creating modernistic design experiences. He says, Put together the clothes from the two craziest cultures, and you get a winning combination! Really cool!
